# Changelog

## [0.3.8]
### Fixed
- build query parameter

## [0.3.7]
### Fixed
- replace all rxjs operators first() with take(1)

## [0.3.6]
### Fixed
- catch unresolvable openapi schema references

## [0.3.5]
### Fixed
- update @rxap/json-schema-to-typescript

## [0.3.4]
### Fixed
- update @rxap/json-schema-to-typescript

## [0.3.3]
### Fixed
- (SchemaValidationMixin): log the schema and value if a validation errors occurs

## [0.3.2]
### Fixed
- (schematics): request body generation

## [0.3.1]
### Fixed
- (SchemaValidationMixin): encode the url path params

## [0.3.0]
### Changed
- (SchemaValidationMixin): ignore header parameter if required

## [0.2.10]
### Fixed
- (SchemaValidationMixin): add support for openapi format options

## [0.2.9]
### Added
- (schematics): rename to generate
- (schematics): add remote method directive generation
### Fixed

## [0.2.8]
